<s> Len, See, this is the struggle I have with this group.  </s>
<s> I think we are spending too much time on the '"R" and not enough time on the "E".  </s>
<s> By focusing on the repair tool, we are putting the onus the user or a third party to try to guess what the author is trying to communicate.  </s>
<s> If we pay a little more attention to evaluation, we can give authors feedback on how to express themselves in multiple, and therefore inclusive, ways.  </s>
<s> There is rarely a one to one correspondence between the same information presented in different modalities, which is why I do not think it can be automated with a tool.  </s>
